content: In the PA channel I see some events for Friendbanking and some events for Power Mapping. What are these? I've never heard of either.
Generally it's talking to friends online.  Not sure what Power Mapping is.  I signed up for a training session on it.
I'm just a new volunteer, so if you really want to know, hopefully someone more knowledgeable will answer.
I'm new too. I live in New York but looking for ways to help in PA.
Friend banking and mapping are ways of using your personal networks to spread the word.
